{
  "openapi": "3.0.0",
  "info": {
    "title": "PrimePix API",
    "version": "1.0.0",
    "description": "\nAPI pública do PrimePix Gateway de Pagamentos PIX.\n\n## Domínios\n- **API**: https://api.primepix.me\n- **Painel**: https://app.primepix.me\n\n## Autenticação\nTodas as requisições devem incluir os headers:\n- `X-API-Key`: Sua chave de API\n- `X-API-Secret`: Seu secret de API (opcional, aumenta segurança)\n\nObtenha suas credenciais em: https://app.primepix.me/settings (aba API)\n\n## Restrição por IP\nVocê pode restringir o acesso à API por IP no painel em Configurações \u003E API.\n\n## Rate Limiting\n- 100 requisições por minuto por IP\n- 1000 requisições por hora por merchant\n\n## Webhooks\nConfigure webhooks para receber notificações em tempo real sobre eventos de transação.\n      ",
    "contact": {
      "name": "Suporte PrimePix",
      "url": "https://app.primepix.me"
    }
  },
  "servers": [
    {
      "url": "https://api.primepix.me/v1",
      "description": "Produção"
    }
  ],
  "security": [
    {
      "apiKey": [],
      "apiSecret": []
    }
  ],
  "tags": [
    {
      "name": "PIX",
      "description": "Operações de cobrança PIX"
    },
    {
      "name": "Transações",
      "description": "Consulta de transações"
    },
    {
      "name": "Saldo",
      "description": "Consulta e saque de saldo"
    },
    {
      "name": "Webhooks",
      "description": "Configuração de webhooks"
    }
  ],
  "paths": {
    "/pix/create": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "PIX"
        ],
        "summary": "Criar cobrança PIX",
        "description": "Gera um QR Code PIX para recebimento de pagamento",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": [
                  "amount"
                ],
                "properties": {
                  "amount": {
                    "type": "number",
                    "description": "Valor da cobrança em reais (mínimo: R$ 1,00)",
                    "example": 100,
                    "minimum": 1
                  },
                  "externalId": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "description": "ID externo para referência no seu sistema",
                    "example": "pedido-12345",
                    "maxLength": 255
                  },
                  "description": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "description": "Descrição da cobrança (aparece no comprovante)",
                    "example": "Pagamento do pedido #12345",
                    "maxLength": 500
                  },
                  "expiresIn": {
                    "type": "integer",
                    "description": "Tempo de expiração em minutos (padrão: 30)",
                    "example": 60,
                    "default": 30,
                    "minimum": 5,
                    "maximum": 1440
                  },
                  "customer": {
                    "type": "object",
                    "description": "Dados do cliente (opcional)",
                    "properties": {
                      "name": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "Nome do cliente",
                        "example": "João da Silva"
                      },
                      "document": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "CPF ou CNPJ do cliente",
                        "example": "123.456.789-00"
                      },
                      "phone": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "Telefone do cliente",
                        "example": "(11) 99999-9999"
                      },
                      "email": {
                        "type": "string",
                        "description": "E-mail do cliente",
                        "example": "joao@email.com"
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              },
              "example": {
                "amount": 150,
                "externalId": "pedido-12345",
                "description": "Compra na loja online",
                "expiresIn": 60,
                "customer": {
                  "name": "João da Silva",
                  "document": "123.456.789-00",
                  "email": "joao@email.com"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Cobrança criada com sucesso",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/PixCreateResponse"
                },
                "example": {
                  "success": true,
                  "data": {
                    "transactionId": 12345,
                    "externalId": "pedido-12345",
                    "qrCode": "00020126580014br.gov.bcb.pix0136a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890520400005303986540515.005802BR5913PRIMEPIX6008SAOPAULO62070503***6304ABCD",
                    "qrCodeBase64": "data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgo...",
                    "amount": 150,
                    "fee": 1.5,
                    "netAmount": 148.5,
                    "status": "pending",
                    "expiresAt": "2025-01-15T16:30:00.000Z"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "Erro de validação",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"
                },
                "example": {
                  "success": false,
                  "error": "Valor mínimo é R$ 1,00"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "401": {
            "description": "Não autorizado",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"
                },
                "example": {
                  "success": false,
                  "error": "Credenciais inválidas"
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "403": {
            "description": "KYC não aprovado",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"
                },
                "example": {
                  "success": false,
                  "error": "Sua conta precisa ser verificada (KYC) para usar a API"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/pix/status/{id}": {
      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "PIX"
        ],
        "summary": "Consultar status da cobrança",
        "description": "Retorna o status atual de uma cobrança PIX",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "id",
            "in": "path",
            "required": true,
            "description": "ID da transação (interno, externo ou VersellPay)",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            },
            "examples": {
              "internal": {
                "value": "12345",
                "summary": "ID interno"
              },
              "external": {
                "value": "pedido-12345",
                "summary": "ID externo"
              }
            }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Status da transação",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/TransactionStatusResponse"
                },
                "example": {
                  "success": true,
                  "data": {
                    "id": 12345,
                    "externalId": "pedido-12345",
                    "amount": 150,
                    "fee": 1.5,
                    "netAmount": 148.5,
                    "status": "completed",
                    "type": "deposit",
                    "description": "Compra na loja online",
                    "customer": {
                      "name": "João da Silva",
                      "document": "123.456.789-00"
                    },
                    "paidAt": "2025-01-15T15:45:30.000Z",
                    "createdAt": "2025-01-15T15:30:00.000Z"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "404": {
            "description": "Transação não encontrada",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/ErrorResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/transactions": {
      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "Transações"
        ],
        "summary": "Listar transações",
        "description": "Retorna lista paginada de transações com filtros opcionais",
        "parameters": [
          {
            "name": "page",
            "in": "query",
            "description": "Página (começa em 1)",
            "schema": {
              "type": "integer",
              "default": 1,
              "minimum": 1
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "limit",
            "in": "query",
            "description": "Itens por página (máximo 100)",
            "schema": {
              "type": "integer",
              "default": 20,
              "minimum": 1,
              "maximum": 100
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "status",
            "in": "query",
            "description": "Filtrar por status",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "enum": [
                "pending",
                "completed",
                "failed",
                "expired",
                "refunded"
              ]
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "type",
            "in": "query",
            "description": "Filtrar por tipo",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "enum": [
                "deposit",
                "withdrawal"
              ]
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "startDate",
            "in": "query",
            "description": "Data inicial (ISO 8601)",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "format": "date-time"
            },
            "example": "2025-01-01T00:00:00Z"
          },
          {
            "name": "endDate",
            "in": "query",
            "description": "Data final (ISO 8601)",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string",
              "format": "date-time"
            },
            "example": "2025-01-31T23:59:59Z"
          },
          {
            "name": "search",
            "in": "query",
            "description": "Buscar por nome, documento ou ID externo",
            "schema": {
              "type": "string"
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "minAmount",
            "in": "query",
            "description": "Valor mínimo",
            "schema": {
              "type": "number"
            }
          },
          {
            "name": "maxAmount",
            "in": "query",
            "description": "Valor máximo",
            "schema": {
              "type": "number"
            }
          }
        ],
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Lista de transações",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/TransactionListResponse"
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/balance": {
      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "Saldo"
        ],
        "summary": "Consultar saldo",
        "description": "Retorna o saldo disponível, pendente e total da conta",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Saldo da conta",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/BalanceResponse"
                },
                "example": {
                  "success": true,
                  "data": {
                    "available": 5000,
                    "pending": 150,
                    "total": 5150,
                    "currency": "BRL"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/withdraw": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "Saldo"
        ],
        "summary": "Solicitar saque",
        "description": "Solicita um saque via PIX para a chave informada",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": [
                  "amount",
                  "pixKey",
                  "pixKeyType"
                ],
                "properties": {
                  "amount": {
                    "type": "number",
                    "description": "Valor do saque em reais",
                    "example": 500,
                    "minimum": 10
                  },
                  "pixKey": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "description": "Chave PIX de destino",
                    "example": "joao@email.com"
                  },
                  "pixKeyType": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "description": "Tipo da chave PIX",
                    "enum": [
                      "CPF",
                      "CNPJ",
                      "EMAIL",
                      "PHONE",
                      "EVP"
                    ],
                    "example": "EMAIL"
                  },
                  "description": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "description": "Descrição do saque",
                    "example": "Saque mensal"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Saque solicitado com sucesso",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "success": {
                      "type": "boolean"
                    },
                    "data": {
                      "type": "object",
                      "properties": {
                        "withdrawalId": {
                          "type": "integer"
                        },
                        "amount": {
                          "type": "number"
                        },
                        "fee": {
                          "type": "number"
                        },
                        "netAmount": {
                          "type": "number"
                        },
                        "status": {
                          "type": "string"
                        },
                        "estimatedCompletion": {
                          "type": "string"
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                },
                "example": {
                  "success": true,
                  "data": {
                    "withdrawalId": 789,
                    "amount": 500,
                    "fee": 2,
                    "netAmount": 498,
                    "status": "pending",
                    "estimatedCompletion": "Em até 24 horas úteis"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          },
          "400": {
            "description": "Saldo insuficiente ou dados inválidos"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "/webhook/configure": {
      "post": {
        "tags": [
          "Webhooks"
        ],
        "summary": "Configurar webhook",
        "description": "Configura uma URL para receber notificações de eventos",
        "requestBody": {
          "required": true,
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "type": "object",
                "required": [
                  "webhookUrl"
                ],
                "properties": {
                  "webhookUrl": {
                    "type": "string",
                    "format": "uri",
                    "description": "URL que receberá os webhooks (HTTPS recomendado)",
                    "example": "https://seusite.com/webhook/primepix"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Webhook configurado",
            "content": {
              "application/json": {
                "schema": {
                  "type": "object",
                  "properties": {
                    "success": {
                      "type": "boolean"
                    },
                    "data": {
                      "type": "object",
                      "properties": {
                        "webhookUrl": {
                          "type": "string"
                        },
                        "webhookSecret": {
                          "type": "string",
                          "description": "Secret para validar assinatura dos webhooks"
                        }
                      }
                    }
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "get": {
        "tags": [
          "Webhooks"
        ],
        "summary": "Consultar webhook",
        "description": "Retorna a configuração atual do webhook",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Configuração do webhook"
          }
        }
      },
      "delete": {
        "tags": [
          "Webhooks"
        ],
        "summary": "Remover webhook",
        "description": "Remove a configuração de webhook",
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Webhook removido"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "components": {
    "securitySchemes": {
      "apiKey": {
        "type": "apiKey",
        "in": "header",
        "name": "X-API-Key",
        "description": "Chave de API obtida no painel"
      },
      "apiSecret": {
        "type": "apiKey",
        "in": "header",
        "name": "X-API-Secret",
        "description": "Secret de API (opcional, aumenta segurança)"
      }
    },
    "schemas": {
      "ErrorResponse": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "success": {
            "type": "boolean",
            "example": false
          },
          "error": {
            "type": "string"
          },
          "code": {
            "type": "string"
          }
        }
      },
      "PixCreateResponse": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "success": {
            "type": "boolean"
          },
          "data": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "transactionId": {
                "type": "integer"
              },
              "externalId": {
                "type": "string"
              },
              "qrCode": {
                "type": "string",
                "description": "Código copia e cola do PIX"
              },
              "qrCodeBase64": {
                "type": "string",
                "description": "QR Code em base64"
              },
              "amount": {
                "type": "number"
              },
              "fee": {
                "type": "number"
              },
              "netAmount": {
                "type": "number"
              },
              "status": {
                "type": "string"
              },
              "expiresAt": {
                "type": "string",
                "format": "date-time"
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "TransactionStatusResponse": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "success": {
            "type": "boolean"
          },
          "data": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "id": {
                "type": "integer"
              },
              "externalId": {
                "type": "string"
              },
              "amount": {
                "type": "number"
              },
              "fee": {
                "type": "number"
              },
              "netAmount": {
                "type": "number"
              },
              "status": {
                "type": "string",
                "enum": [
                  "pending",
                  "completed",
                  "failed",
                  "expired",
                  "refunded"
                ]
              },
              "type": {
                "type": "string",
                "enum": [
                  "deposit",
                  "withdrawal"
                ]
              },
              "description": {
                "type": "string"
              },
              "customer": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                  "name": {
                    "type": "string"
                  },
                  "document": {
                    "type": "string"
                  }
                }
              },
              "paidAt": {
                "type": "string",
                "format": "date-time",
                "nullable": true
              },
              "createdAt": {
                "type": "string",
                "format": "date-time"
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "TransactionListResponse": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "success": {
            "type": "boolean"
          },
          "data": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "transactions": {
                "type": "array",
                "items": {
                  "$ref": "#/components/schemas/TransactionStatusResponse/properties/data"
                }
              },
              "pagination": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                  "page": {
                    "type": "integer"
                  },
                  "limit": {
                    "type": "integer"
                  },
                  "total": {
                    "type": "integer"
                  },
                  "totalPages": {
                    "type": "integer"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "BalanceResponse": {
        "type": "object",
        "properties": {
          "success": {
            "type": "boolean"
          },
          "data": {
            "type": "object",
            "properties": {
              "available": {
                "type": "number",
                "description": "Saldo disponível para saque"
              },
              "pending": {
                "type": "number",
                "description": "Saldo em processamento"
              },
              "total": {
                "type": "number",
                "description": "Saldo total"
              },
              "currency": {
                "type": "string",
                "example": "BRL"
              }
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "WebhookPayload": {
        "type": "object",
        "description": "Payload enviado pelo webhook",
        "properties": {
          "event": {
            "type": "string",
            "description": "Tipo do evento",
            "enum": [
              "transaction.created",
              "transaction.updated",
              "transaction.completed",
              "transaction.failed",
              "transaction.expired",
              "withdrawal.created",
              "withdrawal.completed",
              "withdrawal.failed"
            ]
          },
          "timestamp": {
            "type": "string",
            "format": "date-time",
            "description": "Data/hora do evento (timezone São Paulo)"
          },
          "data": {
            "type": "object",
            "description": "Dados do evento",
            "properties": {
              "transactionId": {
                "type": "integer"
              },
              "externalId": {
                "type": "string"
              },
              "amount": {
                "type": "number"
              },
              "status": {
                "type": "string"
              },
              "previousStatus": {
                "type": "string"
              },
              "customer": {
                "type": "object",
                "properties": {
                  "name": {
                    "type": "string"
                  },
                  "document": {
                    "type": "string"
                  }
                }
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "example": {
          "event": "transaction.completed",
          "timestamp": "2025-01-15T15:45:30-03:00",
          "data": {
            "transactionId": 12345,
            "externalId": "pedido-12345",
            "amount": 150,
            "status": "completed",
            "previousStatus": "pending",
            "customer": {
              "name": "João da Silva",
              "document": "123.456.789-00"
            }
          }
        }
      }
    }
  },
  "webhooks": {
    "transactionUpdated": {
      "post": {
        "summary": "Notificação de transação",
        "description": "\n## Validação de Assinatura\n\nTodos os webhooks incluem o header `X-Webhook-Signature` com uma assinatura HMAC-SHA256.\n\n**Como validar:**\n```javascript\nconst crypto = require('crypto');\n\nfunction validateWebhook(payload, signature, secret) {\n  const expectedSignature = crypto\n    .createHmac('sha256', secret)\n    .update(JSON.stringify(payload))\n    .digest('hex');\n  \n  return crypto.timingSafeEqual(\n    Buffer.from(signature),\n    Buffer.from(expectedSignature)\n  );\n}\n\n// No seu endpoint\napp.post('/webhook/primepix', (req, res) => {\n  const signature = req.headers['x-webhook-signature'];\n  const isValid = validateWebhook(req.body, signature, process.env.PRIMEPIX_WEBHOOK_SECRET);\n  \n  if (!isValid) {\n    return res.status(401).send('Assinatura inválida');\n  }\n  \n  // Processar webhook...\n  const { event, data } = req.body;\n  \n  switch (event) {\n    case 'transaction.completed':\n      // Pagamento confirmado\n      await processPayment(data);\n      break;\n    case 'transaction.failed':\n      // Pagamento falhou\n      await handleFailure(data);\n      break;\n  }\n  \n  res.status(200).send('OK');\n});\n```\n\n## Retry Policy\n\n- Tentamos entregar o webhook até 5 vezes\n- Intervalo entre tentativas: 1min, 2min, 4min, 8min, 16min (backoff exponencial)\n- Seu endpoint deve retornar status 2xx em até 10 segundos\n\n## Eventos Disponíveis\n\n| Evento | Descrição |\n|--------|-----------|\n| `transaction.created` | Nova cobrança criada |\n| `transaction.updated` | Status da transação atualizado |\n| `transaction.completed` | Pagamento confirmado |\n| `transaction.failed` | Pagamento falhou |\n| `transaction.expired` | Cobrança expirou |\n| `withdrawal.created` | Saque solicitado |\n| `withdrawal.completed` | Saque realizado |\n| `withdrawal.failed` | Saque falhou |\n          ",
        "requestBody": {
          "content": {
            "application/json": {
              "schema": {
                "$ref": "#/components/schemas/WebhookPayload"
              }
            }
          }
        },
        "responses": {
          "200": {
            "description": "Webhook recebido com sucesso"
          }
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
